{"tid":531562,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"讓毛，六卷長毛","createTime":"2018-01-17T03:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T03:19:16.000Z","uid":28152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1914829161586699c80104869d101a31ce30b5c","tid":531562,"uid":28152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:19:16.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打<br />\n<br />\n我手頭上有6卷 50米長，1米闊既布。老母說布原產意大利。<br />\n<br />\n毛的成分如下：<br />\n85%羊毛wool<br />\n15%nylon<br />\n<br />\n有興趣的人要自己黎元朗拎，錢方面每卷大約一百蚊。￼ ￼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/111756_48018adf4e44efcf846cc29c9c16209d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F111756_48018adf4e44efcf846cc29c9c16209d.png&h=1682dbe0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}